_header: Saint Agnes woned in Rome so I you tolden ere
Subjects: saints’ lives; Emerentiana (wet nurse to Saint Agnes), saint, life of
_description: Life of ‘St. Emerentiana þe Virgin’, in one MS of the South English Legendary — couplets

Bod779.First Lines:
Seint anneys woned in rome so ich ȝou toldin ereȝhe hadde
                    a fostirsostir þat wit here woned þere…
Bod779.Last Lines:
…Bidde we to Ihesu crist for emerencianus loueþat he vs
                    granten þe blis þat is in heuen aboue
